# When cross-compiling, we want to use the target headers for
# generating dependencies (MAKEDEPCFLAGS), but the host's default
# headers for compiling tools (HOSTCFLAGS).
# Note: We don't put INCLUDEDIRS in HOSTCFLAGS.
